query:
SELECT p.id, p.nome, p.lastActivityAt, p.status,
       hw.id as warning_id, hw.scheduledHibernationDate, hw.notificationSent, hw.hibernated
FROM projects p
LEFT JOIN hibernation_warnings hw ON p.id = hw.projectId AND hw.hibernated = 0
WHERE p.status = 'active'
ORDER BY p.lastActivityAt ASC
LIMIT 5;
